pullRequest.body:
In this PR, we construct the pseudofunctor `ModuleCat.restrictScalarsPseudofunctor : Pseudofunctor (LocallyDiscrete RingCatáµ’áµ–) Cat` which sends a ring `R` to its category of modules: the contravariant functoriality is given
by the restriction of scalars functors. We also define `ModuleCat.extendScalarsPseudofunctor : Pseudofunctor (LocallyDiscrete CommRingCat) Cat`: the covariant functoriality is given by the extension of scalars functors.

---

- [ ] depends on: #18201
